r\ndiv.WordSection1\r\n	{page:WordSection1;}\r\n-->\r\n</style>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal;background:white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:" times="" new="">Guilherme Kominami &eacute; programador, animador, ilustrador, sonhador e pai do pequeno Otto.</span></p>\r\n<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal;background:white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:" times="" new="">Al&eacute;m de ter criado o aplicativo &quot;Mam&atilde;e Pechincha&quot; ele tamb&eacute;m nos presenteou com sua criatividade na anima&ccedil;&atilde;o do Quintal de Trocas</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<object width="0" height="0" id="a96bcbbb-0b58-9c8a-db28-3b8f6a988e83" type="application/gas-events-abn"></object>', '2013-10-08 09:10:52', '2013-10-25 03:10:28', 1, NULL, 5, 7, '2013-10-08 00:00:00'),
